      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am absolutely thrilled to be listing my pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such stunning shape, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s super clean, inside and out\u2014you really have to see it to believe how perfect it is! I'm so excited for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
