    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule with all records meticulously organized. It has been garage-kept under a breathable cover in a climate-controlled environment, never seeing rain or snow. Included are both original keys, the full owner\u2019s manual suite, and untouched factory floor mats. For the buyer who demands absolute perfection, this vehicle stands in a class of its own.",
      "price": 48500.0,
